Selenium---->
    open source automation functional testing framework
    Automation testing
    for the browser testing we use selenium
    selenium python binding provides the access to api
    selenium api---> access to selenium webdriver(browser)
        chrome,firefox,IE,safari,remote

    All the type of web application---> automated with selenium
    but Angular Js website----> selenium will not work
                ----->used Protractor tool      ---> gs lab,calsoft,LT
    but Desktop Application----> selenium2 --->
                ---> sikuli
    selemium--->

Features of selenium--->
    open source
    portable
    Combination of tools
    Easy to understand---> but that we req langauge knw
    Test execution is reduced by time-----> ??
       script----> written time consuming
                any time
                any where

    Test execution can be happen in paraller
    supported multiple langauges---->
            java,.net,c#,python
    supports multiple OS--->win,ios,linux,mac
    support multiple browser----> chrome,firefox,IE,etc

Components of selenium---->

1 Selenium IDE---> intergated developement env
            ---> Tool
            ----> Record and run the script
            ---> every action will recorded and run the action
            --->Only installed firefox
            ---> by default record---> HTML
                    ----> html to other language

2 Selenium RC---> Remote Control
        ---> only work with single browser but web server will open all browser
        ---> selenium 1
        ---> act as API


3 Selenium GRID---> parallel execution
                ---> max 5 browser at a time
                ---> comparatability testing---->all the OS
                ---> to save the execution time

4 Selenium webdriver----> script
                    advanced version of selemium RC
5 SEKENDROID and APPIUM----> to mobile application


